      "text": "ああ、LizNoirらしく、愛の魅力で\nみんなを圧倒してくればいい。さあ、行こう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ just be like LizNoir and overwhelm everyone\nyour Ai charm. Let's go!",
