      "startTime": 61.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_03-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん、本日は新作ゲーム『ラストバレル』の\n発売記念イベントにようこそ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ladies and gentlemen‚ welcome to today's\nlaunch event for the new game \"The Last Barrel\"!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_03-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "このゲームは硬派なFPSゲームなんですけど\n多彩なミッションストーリーモードが特徴です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This game is a hardcore FPS game.\nIt features a variety of mission story modes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_03-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "第三ステージのボスキャラはなんと戦車なんですよ\n私、初めて見た時は驚いちゃいました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The boss character in the third stage is a tank!\nI was surprised when I first saw it!",
        "id": ""
