      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_03-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今では余裕で倒せちゃいますけどね！\nサブウェポンの手榴弾も駆使して瞬殺です！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But now I can beat them with a little time to spare!\nWe also make use of subweapon grenades to kill them instantly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
